’Щ@969197826169bdf00b84c5c6dccb8d4ef5590f440736f1003f7fcf1b2bacd0deЪTitle: title: polars str-replace-all
Path: Examples
Content:
Replaces string in a column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a]; [abac] [abac] [abac]] | polars into-df | polars select (polars col a | polars str-replace-all --pattern a --replace A) | polars collect
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ  a   в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ AbAc в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ AbAc в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ AbAc в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Replaces string
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [abac abac abac] | polars into-df | polars str-replace-all --pattern a --replace A
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ  0   в”Ӯ
